### SQL Search - Basic Text Query
# Simple full-text search with pagination
GET {{base_url}}/search?q=workshop&page=1&size=20

###

### SQL Search - With Location and Category Filters
# Comprehensive filtering by city, country, language, categories
GET {{base_url}}/search?q=internship&city=Київ&country=UA&language=uk&is_remote=false&category=internship&category=workshop&sort_by=deadline_at&order=asc&page=1&size=20

###

### SQL Search - Date Range Filters
# Filter by posted dates, event occurrence dates, and deadlines
GET {{base_url}}/search?posted_from=2025-11-01&posted_to=2025-12-31&occurs_from=2025-12-01&occurs_to=2025-12-31&deadline_after=2025-11-15&page=1&size=20

###

### SQL Search - Remote Events Only
# Filter for remote events with sorting
GET {{base_url}}/search?q=remote&is_remote=true&sort_by=posted_at&order=desc&page=1&size=20

###

### SQL Search - By Category and City
# Find workshops in Kyiv sorted by event start date
GET {{base_url}}/search?city=Київ&category=workshop&sort_by=occurs_from&order=asc&page=1&size=10

###

### SQL Search - Upcoming Deadlines
# Find events with deadlines in the near future
GET {{base_url}}/search?deadline_after=2025-11-15&deadline_before=2025-12-15&sort_by=deadline_at&order=asc&page=1&size=20

